The White House




June 23, 2009

 



Schedule Of Judge Sotomayors Capitol Hill Meeting Today 06/23/2009




THE WHITE HOUSE   Office of the Press Secretary  ___________________________________________________________________  FOR IMMEDIATE RELEASE                                           June 23, 2009  SCHEDULE OF JUDGE SOTOMAYOR’S CAPITOL HILL MEETINGS  TUESDAY, JUNE 23 Today, Judge Sotomayor will visit Capitol Hill to meet with the following Senators: Senator Bob Corker (R-TN)  Senator Tim Johnson (D-SD)  Senator George Voinovich (R-OH)  Senator Jay Rockefeller (D-WV)  Senator Roger Wicker (R-MS)  Senator Mark Warner (D-VA)   ##
